telemetry.event.game_load_times.descript: Afto implapik apu ke Vi uleradeki hur plusbraøze hadji-bystrazma/djongzma, farzaja tid brukena na tonti leo fu spelhadji.

telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc: Fshtona fu hel bystrazma fu Minecraft apu vi per maha spil plus bra per mange fal fu kompju au dbaima-poldai. Fallasku ti brukena per apu vi na se au bidzhau bystrazma fu neofal fu Minecraft.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: Na Vi, glavna shiru katai tid spelabma bruk per shkinne velt, au kawarizma na afto bi tid. Tatoeba, koske antaena neo dekina, os Vi ergo na stordai kawari na netopa fu spelabma, treng anse ka rjetzma jam na veltlesatid.

telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Shiruna oba speltropos (tato spelfal, li mod-ena, auen versho) ainlat ke Vi deki shuchu kawari na tuo tel fu spel ke letstevikti na speldjin.
"Velt-lesajena" ufnepik tsunaga "Velt-kntragena" ufnepik per lera ka mange tid brukena per spel.
telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: Velt rømlesena
telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
Afto implapik tsunaga mit "Velt-lesena" implapik per lera tidatai fu speltid.
Tidatai (na sho au tidleo) farzaena koske veltspeltid owari (shkekso na glavna-ekran, shkekso server kara).
